headline: Baird Q3 2024 Small/Mid Cap Growth Equity Fund Commentary
summary: Baird Small/Mid Cap Growth portfolio increased +6.9% in 3Q, net of fees, compared to the +7.0% increase in our primary benchmark, the Russell 2500 Growth Index.
